{"tid":1484883,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"係台灣有26嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:53:10.000Z","uid":1863,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5120b140a443c77e10e016e27efb4c0d30024f","tid":1484883,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"其實我地一樣可以用我地架車黎做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我目前諗到用瓦通紙板，寫上聲援香港嘅字句，再綁係手臂嘅側面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下，南部182、北部北宜、106、五指，日日都咁多追焦手，我地嘅宣傳就會係各大車版出現，假如以車隊形式出現效果就更佳添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位愛車嘅台灣巴打覺得有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0e807cb6b5eaab96d397b1937f020ba0ceb62d12","tid":1484883,"uid":14810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"學人地掛個環島牌係後面上北宜比人追焦追成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9349932f01df1c7190b7a34b8ae359661f5ce5e0","tid":1484883,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e807cb6b5eaab96d397b1937f020ba0ceb62d12","tid":1484883,"uid":14810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"學人地掛個環島牌係後面上北宜比人追焦追成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"我之後會試，勿起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然台灣人要起我底話咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5330c8b74fad090c6d4c50d0e8b77dcbe1c367","tid":1484883,"uid":1863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEr2kFk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEr2kFk.jpg&h=4f6435d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各位係台灣有車嘅巴打，齊齊貼貼紙加廿匹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}